<style>
  .article_column-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  img.article_column-image {
    overflow: hidden;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
  }
  .article_column-image-border {
    border: 1px solid rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
  }
  .article_column {
      height: max-content;
  }
  .article_column-third {
    width: calc(33.3333334% - 33.3333334px);
  }
  .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 25px);
  }
  .article_column-text-third-top {
    padding-top: 81px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 15px);
  }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .article_column-third {
        width: calc(50% - 15px);
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 81px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 950px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .article_column-half {
      width: 100%
    }
    .article_column-third {
        width: 100%;
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .rebranding_container {
        gap: 40px;
    }
    .article_column-text .h3-heading-pp, .article_column-text .h3-heading-ss {
        text-align: center;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 450px) {
    .article_column-image {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Balenciaga 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        authentication process
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      Authenticating a Balenciaga bag or accessory involves a detailed inspection of several key elements to ensure its authenticity and identify authentic bags. Here are the essential steps to follow:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-center">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-1.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Balenciaga authentication process">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 1</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Check the interior label:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         Look for a metal tag or leather tab inside the bag. Authentic Balenciaga items will have a label that includes the style number and serial number.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-2.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Verify the Style Number and Serial Number to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 2</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Verify the style number and serial number:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Ensure that the numbers on the label match the known formats and styles used by Balenciaga. Additionally, check for the ‘f w’ seasonal identification, which helps verify the authenticity based on the production season.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-3.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Inspect the Hardware to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 3</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Inspect the hardware:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Examine the zippers, buckles, and other hardware for quality and authenticity. Genuine Balenciaga hardware is typically made from high-quality materials and features precise engravings.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-4.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Examine the Stitching and Seams to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 4</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Examine the stitching and seams:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Authentic Balenciaga bags will have even, high-quality stitching. Any irregularities or loose threads can be a sign of a counterfeit item.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-5.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Check the Logo and Branding to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 5</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Check the logo and branding:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Ensure that the logo and branding are accurate and consistent with Balenciaga’s standards. Pay attention to the font, spacing, and placement of the logo.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="body-text tac block-bottom-text w-100">
      By following these steps, you can confidently authenticate a Balenciaga bag or accessory and ensure that you’re investing in a genuine luxury item.
  </p>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Article Three columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns rebranding-wider-section-bottom",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}